headline: CarMax Announces Fourth Quarter Conference Call
summary: RICHMOND, Va., March 20, 2025--CarMax, Inc. (NYSE:KMX) will report its financial results for the fourth quarter ended February 28, 2025 before the market opens on April 10, 2025, and it will host a conference call with investors at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results.

headline: Amazon eyes sales of used cars, Automotive News reports
summary: Amazon (AMZN) is eyeing the sale of used cars as the company continues to refine its new car-shopping platform with customers and dealers in certain U.S. markets, Carly Schaffner of Automotive News reports. Publicly traded companies in the used car space include CarMax (KMX), AutoNation (AN), Vroom (VRM), Carvana (CVNA), and Sonic Automotive (SAH).
